{"tid":83432,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"幾個月前釘嘅耳窿 到宜家都係有時會流血","createTime":"2017-01-16T17:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T04:43:34.000Z","uid":6096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c330fcb6b9b646e071b51d863a09b37178679345","tid":83432,"uid":6096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:23:19.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲知點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日都會腫同流血<br />\n已經成日用藥水<br />\n想問有冇方法可以根治<br />\n又唔想佢埋口<br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78111555204acd0f930b8964291bcbd4a70a068","tid":83432,"uid":12337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"試下戴純銀既耳環<br />\n可能你係易敏感？"},{"pid":"6ce7624cf0680aed3f6234300c9d3f8e98e99f1a","tid":83432,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:26:40.000Z","msg":"釘咗年半都仲有膿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要除咗耳環幾個鐘後面已經有皮生翻好難帶到 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93ad1a36c54a9bc6cca05cf5b474a019fcb71e2","tid":83432,"uid":73002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:30:41.000Z","msg":"我之前試過摸到耳窿有硬塊，就諗住唔帶耳環等個耳窿自己埋口，但係好似隔左兩三個禮拜佢都無埋口然後就自己好返"},{"pid":"ae613f41d6c7a5f6fef4e57a7d012914c5ebab08","tid":83432,"uid":39055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T17:36:40.000Z","msg":"我試過不停滴酒精諗住會好點知爛耳仔<br />\n之後睇醫生先知唔好成日滴酒精，用清水就得<br />\n你可以試下用耳針浸一浸生油再吉入耳仔<br />\nE個方法係我嫲嫲教，我同我d朋友試過都work冇再流血"},{"pid":"21f95cfacb7efd663880499f1e1abf9f327cc0f3","tid":83432,"uid":6096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:11:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我試過不停滴酒精諗住會好點知爛耳仔<br />\n之後睇醫生先知唔好成日滴酒精，用清水就得<br />\n你可以試下用耳針浸一浸生油再吉入耳仔<br />\nE個方法係我嫲嫲教，我同我d朋友試過都work冇再流血</blockquote><br />\n生油係咪煮食油就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d606c28687c3706c234e827404bb8abc1d3734","tid":83432,"uid":64775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:50:18.000Z","msg":"可能係敏感+1"},{"pid":"93854b4e910053785c5b51670765e15f147c97e6","tid":83432,"uid":66150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:18:42.000Z","msg":"釘左3個月<br />\n除左一日穿唔返"},{"pid":"e74a111ef1e4c49a75599b3cc043c152bffd22eb","tid":83432,"uid":49109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:28:34.000Z","msg":"流血就唔好除，一除就好會埋口<br />\n我之前釘完個幾月都係咁，唔好成日搞佢"},{"pid":"29a29a54d29711c8c8c862fa9065a61045839e4f","tid":83432,"uid":5739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"戴果時點少少娥羅納英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}